// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7781 — Mass File Rename (worldleaks)
// Status: test | Level: high | ID: 4248ea37-7852-50d9-9d4f-ee184aea956d

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
